short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily export tydliga (previously Pensum) competition certificates directly from SportAdmin.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
v1.3.2:
Fix for participants lists for 18 gymnasts.

v1.3.1:
Fix for exported participants lists containing a "1" in one of the fields.

v1.3.0:
Export participants lists for the selected gymnasts.

v1.2.0:
Pensum has been acquired by tydliga. Use tydliga.se instead of pensum.se.

v1.1.9:
Scrollable members list.

v1.1.8:
Compatible with new beta version of Sportadmin.

v1.1.7:
Updated Pensum icon.

v1.1.6:
Connect to Pensum using TLS.

v1.1.5:
Detects gymnasts that have group memberships matching "ledarbarn".

v1.1.4:
Detects gymnasts that have group memberships matching "aktiv".

v1.1.3:
Detects gymnasts that have other group memberships than "Gymnast".

v1.1.2:
Should now work with groups containing swedish characters (å, ä, ö).

v1.1.1:
Fixes for Sportadmin changes. Everything should work again.

v1.1.0:
Now supports exporting certificates for "Svenska Cheerleadingförbundet".
